Description: Downloads all the datasets (you can exclude the daily ones or specify a list of those you are targeting specifically) from Kenneth French's Website, read them and convert them to list of xts (time series).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), utils, stats, rvest, xts, xml2, zoo, plyr
